msgid "Scenario VIII: Return to Before the Black Throne"
msgstr "冒险VIII：重返黑色王座"

msgid "Each investigator suffers 1 physical trauma and 1 mental trauma, as the nightmarish work takes its toll on their bodies and minds."
msgstr "每位调查员因为噩梦般的劳作而身心受创，受到1点肉体创伤和1点精神创伤。"

msgid "When building the act deck, replace the original version of act 3 with the new version included in the <i>Return to Before the Black Throne</i> encounter set. Remove the original version from the game."
msgstr "在构建场景牌堆时，用<i>重返黑色王座</i>遭遇组中的新版场景3代替原版场景3。将原版场景3从游戏中移除。"

msgid "When building the Cosmos, be sure to include the 3 new Cosmos locations included in the <i>Return to Before the Black Throne</i> encounter set."
msgstr "在构建“宇宙”时，加入<i>重返黑色王座</i>遭遇组中的3张新的宇宙地点。"

msgid "When the game begins, the investigators may remove 2 resources from the scenario reference card to have each investigator begin the game with the Nightgaunt Steed story asset in play. Remove each remaining Nightgaunt Steed from the game."
msgstr "在游戏开始时，调查员可以从冒险辅助卡上移除2资源，使开始时每位调查员场上有夜魇坐骑剧情支援。将所有剩余的夜魇坐骑从游戏中移除。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"Wheel of Fortune · X\" in the reversed position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是逆位的“命运之轮·X”。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"Wheel of Fortune · X\" in the upright position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是正位的“命运之轮·X”。"

msgid ""
"This is it. The end of all things, and the nighted throne of the being known as Azathoth. You know there is no sense in harming it—if such a thing can even suffer harm—so you set about finding another way to prevent it from waking. You understand now that the spirits you saw in Hangman's Hill were trying to warn you. Trying to drive you away from the same path Keziah led them down so many years ago. Anette's incantation served as this creature's alarm, and so you shall transform it into a lullaby.\n"
"It takes ages for you to find within these vast timeless halls the spirit that knows how to reverse the incantation. And it takes even longer to drag the words from its hollow throat. But together, you speak aloud the rite that ends Keziah's work once and for all. Azathoth slumbers once more, though you know it will not last forever. With your task complete, you turn and face the darkness, summoning your steed. It is time to go home."
msgstr ""
"终于到了。万物归一，还有名为阿撒托斯的存在的漆黑王座。你知道伤害它毫无意义——如果这样的东西也能被伤害——于是你开始寻找另一种方法来防止它醒来。你现在明白了，你在绞刑者山丘看到的鬼魂是在试图警告你，试图让你不要重蹈多年前凯夏带它们经历的覆辙。安妮特的咒语是这个怪物的闹钟，而你要把它转变成一首催眠曲。\n"
"你在这些巨大而永恒的大厅中花了很长时间，才找到了知晓如何反转咒语的灵魂。而让它空洞的喉咙发声则花了更长时间。但你们还是共同大声念出了仪式，永远终结了凯夏的咒语。阿撒托斯又一次陷入沉眠，但你知道它不会永远地睡下去。任务完成后，你转身面对黑暗，召唤你的坐骑。是时候回家了。"
